<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>For Ashtalfa ❤️</title>

<style>

*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:linear-gradient(
        135deg,
        #0f172a,
        #312e81,
        #7c3aed,
        #db2777
    );
    min-height:100vh;
    color:white;
    overflow-x:hidden;
}

.container{
    width:90%;
    max-width:1000px;
    margin:40px auto;
    padding:40px;
    text-align:center;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    backdrop-filter:blur(15px);
    border-radius:25px;
    box-shadow:0 0 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}

h1{
    font-size:3rem;
    margin-bottom:10px;
    animation:glow 2s infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes glow{
    from{
        text-shadow:0 0 10px #ff9ecf;
    }
    to{
        text-shadow:0 0 25px #ffd6e8;
    }
}

.nickname{
    font-size:1.3rem;
    color:#ffd6e8;
    margin-bottom:25px;
}

.message{
    font-size:1.15rem;
    line-height:1.9;
    margin-bottom:30px;
}

.special-section{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));
    gap:20px;
    margin-top:30px;
}

.card{
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    padding:25px;
    border-radius:20px;
    text-align:left;
    transition:0.3s;
}

.card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow:0 0 25px rgba(255,182,193,0.3);
}

.card h2{
    color:#ffb6d9;
    margin-bottom:12px;
}

.btn{
    margin:15px;
    padding:14px 30px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:30px;
    background:#ec4899;
    color:white;
    cursor:pointer;
    font-size:1rem;
    transition:0.3s;
}

.btn:hover{
    transform:scale(1.08);
}

.surprise{
    display:none;
    margin-top:20px;
    font-size:1.3rem;
    color:#ffd700;
}

.modal{
    display:none;
    position:fixed;
    inset:0;
    background:rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    padding:20px;
}

.modal-content{
    background:#1e293b;
    width:90%;
    max-width:700px;
    padding:30px;
    border-radius:20px;
    text-align:left;
    line-height:1.9;
}

.close{
    float:right;
    cursor:pointer;
    font-size:30px;
}

.heart{
    position:fixed;
    animation:float 6s linear forwards;
}

@keyframes float{
    from{
        transform:translateY(100vh);
        opacity:1;
    }
    to{
        transform:translateY(-120px);
        opacity:0;
    }
}

.footer{
    margin-top:35px;
    color:#fbcfe8;
}

</style>

</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

```
<h1>❤️ For Ashtalfa ❤️</h1>

<div class="nickname">
    Ash • Cutie • Ashuu • She ✨
</div>

<div class="message">

    Dear Ashtalfa,

    <br><br>

