    but there are things I never want you to forget.

    <br><br>

    You are genuinely one of the most special people I know.

    <br><br>

    Whether I call you Ash, Cutie, Ashuu, or She,
    every name reminds me of someone kind, caring, beautiful,
    and unforgettable.

    <br><br>

    I pray that Allah fills your life with happiness,
    success, peace, good health, and endless blessings.

    <br><br>

    <i>
    "Allah tumhari zindagi ko khushiyon, barkaton aur sukoon se bhar de.
    Tum hamesha muskurati raho aur har qadam par kamyabi tumhara muqaddar bane."
    </i>

</div>

<div class="special-section">

    <div class="card">
        <h2>😊 Your Smile</h2>
        <p>
            Your smile is honestly one of the most beautiful things about you.
            It has a way of making everything feel lighter and brighter.
            No matter how difficult a day may be,
            seeing you smile feels like seeing sunshine after a storm.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>💖 Your Character</h2>
        <p>
            What makes you special isn't just your beauty,
            it's your heart.
            Your kindness, patience, understanding,
            and the way you care about people
