            and every bit of understanding you have shown.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>🌹 A Dua For You</h2>
        <p>
            May Allah protect your heart,
            guide your steps,
            bless your future,
            and grant you happiness wherever life takes you.

            <br><br>

            <i>
            Allah tumhari har dua qubool farmaye,
            tumhein har pareshani se bachaye,
