            Ameen.
            </i>
        </p>
    </div>

</div>

<button class="btn" onclick="showSurprise()">
    ✨ Open Surprise
</button>

<button class="btn" onclick="openLetter()">
    💌 Read My Letter
</button>

<div class="surprise" id="surprise">
    ❤️ Ashuu, you are appreciated more than you know. ❤️
    <br><br>
    🌹 Never forget how special you are. 🌹
    <br><br>
    ✨ Keep smiling, Cutie. ✨
</div>

<div class="footer">
    Made with ❤️ for Ashtalfa
</div>
```

</div>

<div class="modal" id="letterModal">

```
<div class="modal-content">

    <span class="close" onclick="closeLetter()">&times;</span>

    <h2>💌 A Personal Letter</h2>

    <br>

    Dear Ash,

    <br><br>

    If there is one thing I want you to know,
    it is that you deserve every good thing life has to offer.

    <br><br>

    You deserve happiness when days are difficult,
    peace when life feels overwhelming,
    and success in every dream you work hard for.

    <br><br>

    Thank you for your kindness.
    Thank you for your patience.
    Thank you for being yourself.

    <br><br>

    And thank you for the times you chose understanding
    when it would have been easier not to.

    <br><br>

    No matter what happens,
    never forget that you are valuable,
    appreciated,
    and truly special.

    <br><br>

    ❤️

</div>
```

</div>

<script>

function showSurprise(){

    document.getElementById("surprise").style.display="block";

    for(let i=0;i<70;i++){

        let heart=document.createElement("div");

        heart.classList.add("heart");
        heart.innerHTML="💖";

        heart.style.left=Math.random()*100+"vw";
        heart.style.fontSize=(15+Math.random()*25)+"px";

        document.body.appendChild(heart);

        setTimeout(()=>{
            heart.remove();
        },6000);
    }
}

function openLetter(){
    document.getElementById("letterModal").style.display="flex";
}

function closeLetter(){
    document.getElementById("letterModal").style.display="none";
}

window.onclick=function(event){

    const modal=document.getElementById("letterModal");

    if(event.target===modal){
        modal.style.display="none";
    }
}

</script>

</body>
</html>
